This is package is the result of an architecture refactoring of the
neurospaces package.

For installation, refer to the neurospaces HOWTO.outline document.
Most perl packages mentioned overthere are not needed for neurospaces,
but for are needed for using the studio package.

- Bugfix: added renderer font.
- Modularized the renderer's external object facilities.
- Mapped T_sym_segment to a GUI component.
- Allowed to give multiple conditions to bin/neurospaces,
  for improved model queries.
- Bugfixes for the overview extractor.
- Added 'Quit' button.
- Cleanup in the rendering engine.
